  "2336810": {
    "name": "Squad Tactics",
    "steam_appid": 2336810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A portal to another world has opened, releasing an essence that corrupts everything it touches. It takes control of all—humans and demons, the living and the undead—twisting them into a growing army bent on conquering the world.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The world stands on the brink, and only you can stop the tide. Level up your Hero, recruit loyal minions, and forge the perfect Squad before venturing into the Portal to strike at the heart of the threat!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Key Features:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deep Tactical Combat</strong> – Every move matters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>12 Unique Hero Classes</strong> – Endless possible combinations via Multi-Class system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>40+ Minion Types</strong> – From fierce beasts to spell-slinging demons, build your dream Squad from a massive roster.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explosive Combos &amp; Synergies</strong> – Layer attacks, abilities, reactions, and spells for devastating effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tons of Loot &amp; Relics</strong> – Equip your Hero with powerful gear and game-changing artifacts to reshape every run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Replayability</strong> – Procedural challenges, dynamic enemies, and limitless combinations ensure every run is unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336810/extras/53b63c8a318326a570428df82033d4ad.avif?t=1758031591\" width=600 height=411 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Positioning &amp; Orientation</strong>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flank for bonus damage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shield up and reduce frontal hits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Block line-of-sight, drag enemies out of formation, and dominate the battlefield   </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336810/extras/45044f0b66b808c09245e28ab8260c8e.avif?t=1758031591\" width=600 height=443 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Melee Engagement</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lock enemies in place and punish those who flee</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support allies by locking down targets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn when to hold your ground—and when to break away </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336810/extras/4646b8c75bf04b4cf0a286b1804bb62d.avif?t=1758031591\" width=600 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Momentum &amp; Stability</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Momentum fuels offense; Stability powers defense</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both fluctuate constantly—read the battlefield and adapt on the fly</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the rhythm of combat: strike hard, hold firm, and know when to switch gears   </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrades, Mid-Match Evolution</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn Upgrade Points in battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose evolving specializations for every Minion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock powerful Hero Upgrades and pivot your strategy mid-fight</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336810/extras/0f33d54187153a159fe323e97fce4296.avif?t=1758031591\" width=600 height=485 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Combat Types</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skirmish</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casual, chaotic battles with dynamic AI behavior and random terrain</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minions may come and go—adapt on the fly</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Squad Duel</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Competitive, perfectly mirrored maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your Hero at all costs—enemy Minions will die for theirs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hero Duel</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense 1v1 showdown in a tiny arena.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No backup. No escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless waves. Limited time. Just survive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Game Modes</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight through 6 pre-defined Regions with unique features, each with an unique Boss randomly assigned, to unlock the Final Region.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The order in which you fought the Bosses will shape the Final Boss that you must defeat to win the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Winning will unlock one higher difficulty level</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless:</strong><br>Choose between 3 randomly generated Regions with randomized features. Once cleared, you get 3 new choices, and so on infinitely.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Difficulty increases sharply after each Region and it doesn't end until you lose. See how far you can make it!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenges:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create the perfect Squad by freely selecting any Heroes, Minions, Items and Relics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your Squad against a wide variety of pre-defined challenges</p></li></ul>",
